  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Entities
    Trivial utility class for Entities.
    NazgulEntity
    Abstract superclass of all Nazgul-style Entity classes, holding commonly used mechanics for equality, cloning and validation.
    NazgulMutableIdEntity
    Abstract superclass for Entities where a need exists to alter the ID of a NazgulEntity after the required construction.
